    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Al-le-lu-i--a, al--le-lu----i----a, al----le--lu-------i--a. \n\nThe Lord hear thee in the day of af-flic-tion; the Name of the God of Ja--cob___ de-fend__ thee.\n\nAl-le-lu-i--a, al--le-lu----i----a, al----le--lu-------i--a._\n\nO_ Lord, save the king, and heark-en un-to us in the day when we call___ up-on__ Thee.\n\nAl-le-lu-i--a, al--le-lu----i----a, al----le--lu-------i--a.____"
    }
